  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study seeks to study the effectiveness of a short mindfulness based pulmonary
      rehabilitation program prior to a surgical resection in patients with lung cancer and severe
      Chronic Obstructive Lung Disease (COPD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
